FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778186665
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to mother with
OL,4,C'biggest heart' killed in Bristol
OL,5,Cexplosion
OL,7,FSeveral police units were dispatched
OL,8,Fto the address while the caller stayed
OL,9,Fon the line. Before police arrived, an
OL,10,Fexplosion occurred which killed Jo and
OL,11,Fher former partner Ryan Kelly, as well
OL,12,Fas injuring a further three people,
OL,13,Fincluding a child.
OL,15,FIn a tribute released by Jo's family
OL,16,Fthey described her legacy to be of
OL,17,Flove, compassion and strength which
OL,18,Fwill never be forgotten.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778186665
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to mother with
OL,4,C'biggest heart' killed in Bristol
OL,5,Cexplosion
OL,7,F"Joanne brought warmth, kindness, and
OL,8,Fstrength into the lives of countless
OL,9,Fpeople.
OL,11,F"Her loving presence will be missed
OL,12,Fmore than words can ever express, but
OL,13,Fher memory will forever remain in our
OL,14,Fhearts."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
